    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in mint condition. The exterior is free of scratches, dents, and paint defects. The interior shows no signs of wear \u2014 upholstery, trim, and all surfaces are in like-new condition. All mechanical systems are fully functional and performing as expected. This vehicle has been well-maintained and presents as new.",
      "price": 46000.0,
